DOMESTICSERVICEBALANCE.modalContent: RUT deduction is a tax deduction for household services, such as move help and cleaning. If you are entitled to RUT deduction, you only pay 50 % of the labor cost.<1 /><1 />ROT deduction is a tax deduction for renovation, maintenance and reconstruction. If you are entitled to ROT deduction, you pay 70 % of the labor cost.<1 /><1 />The maximum amount for RUT and ROT deduction is 75 000 kronor per year and person (of which a maximum of 50 000 can be ROT deduction).<1 /><1 />You can get info from the Swedish Tax Agency, if you want to see your current RUT balance here at Flyttsmart.<0 href="https://www.skatteverket.se/privat/fastigheterochbostad/rotarbeteochrutarbete.4.2e56d4ba1202f95012080002966.html" target="_blank">Read more at the Swedish Tax Agency</0> web page.
DOMESTICSERVICEBALANCE.modalLink: Read more about ROT and RUT deduction
